    "destruction": "To destroy the *Lung Bloodstone*, a worshipper of Arazni must willingly impale themself with the *Bloodstone\u2019s* horned figurehead, dealing themselves 3d6 piercing damage and 3d6 persistent bleed damage. The *Lung Bloodstone* then evaporates into a cloud of noxious vapors, as *toxic cloud* (DC 28), that follows the creature that destroyed the *Bloodstone* for its duration.",
